# Animation Files

This directory should contain the following video files from Storyset:

## Required Files (Download from Storyset - Free Account Needed)

### 1. browser-stats-rafiki.mp4
- URL: https://storyset.com/illustration/browser-stats/rafiki
- Used in: Card 1 & Card 2 ("Bạn không xây dựng mọi thứ một mình" & "Thu nhập cần được đo lường minh bạch")
- Format: MP4 video
- Settings: Loop, Auto-play

### 2. business-decisions-bro.mp4
- URL: https://storyset.com/illustration/business-decisions/bro
- Used in: Card 3 ("Dữ liệu được phục vụ cho quyết định của bạn")
- Format: MP4 video
- Settings: Loop, Auto-play

## How to Download:

1. Go to Storyset website (free account required)
2. Search for the illustration by name
3. Click "Download" → Choose "Video" or "MP4" format
4. Save to this directory

## Temporary Solution:

If you don't have Storyset account yet, the code will fall back to static SVG images:
- /images/browser-stats-rafiki-1.svg
- /images/browser-stats-rafiki-2.svg
- /images/business-decisions-bro.svg
